description:
This is vanone atelier&rsquo;s lightweight sheer fabric offers just the right amount of transparency without feeling overwhelming. It drapes beautifully with excellent stretch, providing a flowing and comfortable fit. Designed with a moderate boat neck neckline, it can be paired with a sleeveless top for a coordinated look, offering a definite focal point.
&nbsp;
- Perfect for daily wear- Can be paired with different bottoms to create various looks- A basic item that complements any outfit well
